    "body": "## User visual authority\n\nThe current user visual acceptance is FAIL for Stage 6 items 2 and 3, despite prior technical smoke PASS. Exact observed failures:\n- Boomer still visibly showed `отвали`, `свалить`, `вброс`;\n- `заслать` and chat placeholder `пиши по теме` were identical across profiles;\n- Millennial `Уйти: 1` did not identify the currency/cost meaning;\n- stat toasts repeated the same stat symbols already present at their anchors;\n- Zoomer and Alpha were not meaningfully distinguishable in visible UI.\n\nStage 6 remains NOT COMPLETE until the user visually rechecks the repaired game and explicitly accepts it.\n\n## Root causes on base main\n\nExact base: `87fd85c85409c68b67b932438cd798904f8e4722`.\n\n- `index.html` hardcodes chat placeholder/send labels.\n- `ui-dm.js` hardcodes `Вброс` / `Ответка` on argument badges.\n- `ui-events.js` hardcodes `Отвали` / `Свалить` in escape event titles/results.\n- `Data.TEXTS.millennial` aliases legacy `genz`, whose escape label is `Уйти: {X}` without currency marker.\n- Zoomer and Alpha share a broad inherited baseline, leaving too few visible differences on common surfaces.\n- shared system copy contains `Не хватает 💰 на Свалить.` and can leak through fallback routing.\n- stat toasts are anchored to stat icons while toast text may repeat the same icon.\n\n## Canon-safe repair v2\n\nAdd a late-load presentation-only repair module, mirrored byte-identically, loaded after existing UI modules and before dev checks. It:\n- installs distinct visible hardcoded-control copy for Millennial / Zoomer / Alpha / Boomer;\n- realigns only inherited/shared profile dictionary surfaces;\n- preserves the exact accepted PR #245 Alpha frozen-copy keys (`escape_button_label`, `teach_sent_dm`, `teach_sent_chat`, `invite_open_hint`, `invite_invalid`);\n- adds `alphaFrozenCopyPreserved` as a fail-closed smoke check;\n- makes Millennial escape cost explicitly show `💰`;\n- differentiates Zoomer slang surfaces from Alpha terse-neutral inherited/shared surfaces without replacing Alpha frozen-copy outputs;\n- routes known shared escape/training leaks for Millennial/Zoomer/Boomer while leaving Alpha frozen system routing untouched;\n- removes duplicate own-stat icons from stat toast text while preserving the anchor icon;\n- rewrites only known hardcoded escape-event presentation terms for non-Zoomer profiles;\n- synchronizes hardcoded chat/DM/header/action labels after UI renders/profile changes, with semantic label variants so switching profiles does not retain the prior profile's transformed label;\n- exposes `Game.__DEV.smokeStage6FinalVisualToneRepairOnce()`.\n\nNo economy, battle rules, NPC behavior, persistence, state semantics, prices, handlers, or conflict outcomes are changed.\n\n## Exact final diff\n\nChanged paths exactly four:\n- `AsyncScene/Web/ui/ui-profile-visual-tone-repair.js`\n- `docs/ui/ui-profile-visual-tone-repair.js`\n- `AsyncScene/Web/index.html`\n- `docs/index.html`\n\nRepair-module mirrors are byte-identical at blob `a0e0b0451e2e0e216863fc8962a7f0a9b676801c`.\nIndex mirrors are byte-identical at blob `5bd88d8ac8c79d05c55fd58ba334829ffa96f82b`.\nEach index changes by exactly one added script tag.\n\nRuntime/user visual acceptance remains pending after merge.",
